7 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to redefine how
8 recidivism is calculated and establishes a graduated classification system to
9 track individuals who recidivate. The bill also proposes establishing
10 definitions, calculations, and classification systems to measure individuals who
11 commit repeat violent offenses.
