14 Sec. 2. 28 V.S.A. § 4 is amended to read:
15 § 4. STANDARD MEASURE AND CLASSIFICATIONS OF RECIDIVISM;
16 REPEAT VIOLENT OFFENDERS
17 (a) Recidivism.
18 (1) Classifications. The Department shall calculate classify the rate type
19 of recidivism based upon offenders persons who are sentenced to more than
20 one year of incarceration who, after release from incarceration, return to prison
21 within three years for a conviction for a new offense or a violation of
